### AI health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Backend vitals - Normal
POST http://localhost:5000/api/v1/vitals/receive
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "PUT_REAL_PATIENT_ID_HERE",
  "heartRate": 78,
  "spo2": 98,
  "temperature": 36.8,
  "source": "sensor-simulator"
}

